      • EtsiRegion

        public Ipj_Error EtsiRegion(Enums.Regulatory_Region etsiRegion)
        Sets the current ETSI Enums.Regulatory_Region
        With this function, the Enums.Regulatory_Region can be switched from ETSI_EN_302_208 to INDIA_865_867_MHZ and vice versa.
        Only allowed for modules with Enums.DeviceCertification.ETSI

        Ipj_Error
